data.description: KITCHEN IS A DREAM! Gleaming hardwood floors throughout… Two story Foyer with catwalk greets you as you enter. Expansive Family Room w/natural gas FP for those cozy winter nights overlooks chef’s Kitchen with ss appls, glass tile b. splash and white cabs. Primary Suite at the top of the stairs has a gorgeous walk-in closet, rain shower & garden tub w/private view of flowering trees. IN-LAW OR GUEST SUITE on first floor! Second floor boasts two more bedrooms and an oversized bonus room currently used as a fifth bedroom, as well as the third full bathroom. Large Garage with potential for loft storage. Shed, multiple patios, deck, and shaded grilling station are great for entertaining. Landscaped, fenced lot has a beautiful mature fig tree and borders woods that cannot be developed providing PERMANENT PRIVACY.  Peaceful neighborhood close to Buffaloe Road Aquatic Center, shopping and other amenities. SS appliances and stacked WD convey. MUST SEE! Special VA Financing perks for VA Buyer... Please call Listing Agent for details!
